Package: bloomsky
Type: Package
Title: Tools to Work with 'BloomSky' Weather Station Data
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2017-04-18
Author: Bob Rudis (bob@rud.is)
Maintainer: Bob Rudis <bob@rud.is>
Description: The 'BloomSky' weather station has a cloud service <https://www.bloomsky.com/> 
    that centralizes data collection and provides a user interface for interactive data 
    viewing as well as an 'API'. Tools are provided to work with the underlying weather 
    data feeds from the site.
URL: https://github.com/hrbrmstr/bloomsky
BugReports: https://github.com/hrbrmstr/bloomsky/issues
License: AGPL
Suggests:
    testthat,
    covr
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports:
    purrr,
    httr,
    dplyr,
    jsonlite
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
